&lt;li&gt;Build long-term relationships with key channel sources&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and monitor interviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Form sector expertise through regular and consistent research to remain up-to-date on industry trends and news&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For this role, we are looking for proficient German speakers (C1/C2 levels)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
